net v5-home-j4-status-slot v5-native-hal-owner.home-status-slot-04 => joint.4.v5-bus-home-status-slot
net v5-home-j4-axis-code v5-native-hal-owner.home-axis-code-04 => joint.4.v5-bus-home-axis-code
